        "created_at": "2024-07-03T17:06:00.487Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Is there a way to get a close approximation of a size of all keys (or values) for a given record type?</p>\n<p>I see <code>SizeStatisticsCollector</code> but this is essentially iterating all records right? I just need a close approximation of the size for a given record type.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 2,
        "updated_at": "2024-07-03T17:06:00.487Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
